            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1945-11-27T19:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1944-07-17T00:00:00-05:00" n="312" subtype="editorial-note" type="document" xml:id="d312">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>The only record of the substance of this meeting that has been found is in
                        <persName corresp="#p_SERJ1">Stettinius</persName>, <ref target="#pg_67">pp.
                        67</ref>–<ref target="#pg_68">68</ref>. The meeting lasted until “almost
                    midnight”. The information given here as to the meeting and the participants is
                    taken from <persName corresp="#p_SERJ1">Stettinius</persName>, <ref target="#pg_67">p. 67</ref>.</p>
            </div>
